  Lun7 hit-peng5 e5 Soan-to7-hoe7 u7 thang chhiaN2 Bok8-su kap Thoan5-to7 e5 khi3 Kim-mng5 tak8 sou2-chai7 thoan5; m7-na7 sou2-hui3 u7 kau3-giah8, koh u7 chhun chheng-goa7 khou. Che si7 gau5 siat tak8-hang7 e5 hoat-tou7 chiah e7 an2-ni. 
  E7-mng5 e5 tui3-bin7 chiu7-si7 Kou2-long7-su7, ti7-hia u7 chit8-keng Toa7-oh8, mia5 kio3 Hoe5-lan5-chai; hak8-seng 30 lian5 e5, si7 3 e5 kong-hoe7 hap8 cho3-hoe2 teh ka3. Ia7 u7 Sim5-goan5 Tiong-oh8 tng5, hak8-seng 60 goa7 e5; chiong-theng5 u7 ka3 Eng-bun5 kap KoaN-oe7, mui2-ni5 chit8-lang5 thiap 40 khou. Koh u7 chit8-keng Eng-hoa Chu-iN7; hak8-seng pah-si3-gou7 lang5. Ki5-u5 chhin-chhiuN7 Lu2-oh8, Sio2-oh8, sng3 be7-liau2. Chong2-kong7 ti7 Kou2-long7-su7 e5 oh8-tng5, pi2 pat8 sou2-chai7 siang7 te7-it che7. 
  Lun7 Chiang-chiu siaN5 e5 kau3-hoe7, si7 Bi2-kok e5 TiuN2-lo2-kau3 siat e5. Ti7 Tang-poaN2-au7-ke u7 chit8-keng pai3-tng5, tu2-ho2 kap Thian-chu2-kau3 tui3-bin7. Pun2-te7 Bok8-su Ong5 Lim5-Kak si7 siau3-lian5 lang5. Pai3-tng5 iong5-un2 si3-pah8-goa7 lang5. Lai7-bin7 u7 chit8-keng sio2-oh8-tng5, kau3-oan5 3 lang5. Thoan5-to7 2 lang5, TiuN2-lo2 4 lang5, Chip-su7 5,6 lang5. Tiong-kan u7 chit8-e5 TiuN2-lo2 siN3 Tan5 mia5 Khe2-ju7, i-e5 sio2-ti7 si7 Ki2-jin5, i pun2-sin cho3 I-seng, ti7 le2-pai3-jit8 i e5 kang cho3 put-chi2 chiau5-kau3. Chiau3 sou2 thiaN ti7 tak8 le2-pai3-jit8, tui3 9 tiam2 lai5 kau3 12 tiam2; e7-tau3 tui3 2 tiam2 lai5 kau3 4 tiam2; e5-hng koh tui3 7 tiam2 poaN3 lai5 kau3 9 tiam2. I cho3 TiuN2-lo2 e5 bou5-iuN7, che7-che7 lang5 keng3-hok8 i. 
  Chiau3 khoaN3 chit-e5 kau3-hoe7 chin oah8-tang7. Ti7 teng2-pou 9 tiam2 poaN3 cho3 sio2 le2-pai3, kau3 10 tiam2 toa7 le2-pai3; e7-pou 2 tiam2 cho3 Chu2-jit8-oh8; hiaN-ti7 chi2-moe7 hun-cho3 chiaN5-chap8 sou2-chai7 teh thak8 Seng3-chheh. Kau3 3 tiam2 chiaN3 toa7 le2-pai3, poaN3-tiam2 cheng ku2 chiu7 soah. Kau3 e5-hng 7 tiam2 poaN3 koh chu7-chip8 thak8 Seng3-chheh; kau3 8 tiam2 u7 chit8 lang5 cho3 Chu2-li2, chhoa7 cheng3-lang5 le2-pai3, au7-lai5 hek8-si7 ki5-to2, hek8-si7 chiong to7-li2 bian2-le7 kui2-ku3, mia5 cho3 Hu2-tek-hoe7; chiu7-si7 pang-chan7 tek-heng7 e5 i3-su3. Hit me5-hng chu7-chip8 u7 pah-goa7 lang5, khoaN3 liau2 chin lau7-jiat8, goan2 e5 sim put-chi2 hoaN-hi2. Ti7 pai3-tng5 tui3-bin7 u7 khui chit8-keng chheh-pang5, tiam3-ho7 kio3-cho3 Ek-bun5 su-sek, m7-si7 chiong chheh teh be7 lang5 e5 chiN5, i3-su3 si7 pai5-liat8 che7-che7 hang7 e5 chheh hou7 lang5 tak8 jit8 lai5 khoaN3. Che ia7-si7 chit8-hang7 thang chan7 lang5 bat to7-li2. 
  Chiau3 khoaN3 chit-e5 kau3-hoe7 chiah heng-khi2, bok8-koai3 ki5-jian5, in-ui7 tng-chit-e5 lang5 tang5-sim chin oah8-tang7 gau5 siat-hoat. U7 thiaN-kiN3 kui2-na7 e5 TiuN2-lo2 long2 oh8 i-seng, khui tiam3 ia7 li7 bo5 loa7-hng7; iau2-ku2 ti7 seng3-jit8 e7 saN-ho5 saN-thiaN3 saN-chan7 cho3 kang, bo5 chhin-chhiuN7 hit ho7 kan-ta kou3 ka-ti7 a2-si7 tong5-ge7 siong-tou3, chin-chiaN3 thang hou7 lang5 keng3-hok8. 
  Ti7 Chiang-chiu siaN5-lai7 u7 chit8 keng Tiong-se oh8, hak8-seng chin-che7 lang5, lai7-bin7 ka3-hoat put-chi2 chiau5-pi7, long2-si7 kau3-hoe7 lai7 e5 lang5 kou2-bu2 te5-gin5 ka-ti7 siat-hoat, m7-bian2 oa2-kho3 goa7-kok lang5. 
(Tai5-lam5 Hu2-siaN5 Kau3-hoe7-po3 te7 266~269 koan3, 1907 ni5 5~8 geh8)
